Package: rWCVPdata
Type: Package
Title: Data from the 'World Checklist of Vascular Plants'
Version: 0.5.0
Authors@R: c(person("Matilda","Brown",,"m.brown2@kew.org",role=c("aut","cre","cph")),
             person("Barnaby","Walker",,"b.walker@kew.org",role=c("aut")))
Maintainer: Matilda Brown <m.brown2@kew.org>
Description: Distributes snapshots of the 'World Checklist of Vascular Plants'
    (WCVP) database. Designed to be used in conjunction with the 'rWCVP' 
    package for taxonomic and distributional analysis. Provides essential 
    data for vascular plant research locally in 'R'.
